<a name="guess-the-file"><h2>Guess the file</h2></a>
<p class="Stats"><time datetime="2018-12">December 2018</time> • $(loc ../gists/what_file what_file) • bash • Unlicense</p>
<p>Explore a snippet of source code like a dungeon in a <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roguelike">roguelike</a>.</p>
<p>Can you guess which programming language or project a file comes from?</p>
<p>Move with WASD or HJKL, and as soon as you think you know what it is, press Enter and choose your answer from three options.</p>
<ul class="ProjectLinks Separator">
<li><a href="https://gist.github.com/markusfisch/0316a791501e383b195d0fce6a30b5b0" class="Primary">Source</a></li>
</ul></article>
